{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2011/02/interesting-site-carpenter/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/pcandinternet/","name":"计算机与网络"}],"tags":[{"name":"DIY","path":"/tag/diy/"},{"name":"全景","path":"/tag/panorama/"},{"name":"技术","path":"/tag/technology/"},{"name":"摄影","path":"/tag/photography/"},{"name":"趣站","path":"/tag/interest-site/"}],"featured_media":null,"path":"/2011/02/interesting-site-carpenter/","date":"2011-02-24T13:45:00.000Z","excerpt":"在网上晃悠，发现一个有趣的网站，www.sentex.net/~mwandel/ 首页上这位大叔就是Matth … ","title":"趣站推荐——全才木工大叔的发明创造","content":"<p>在网上晃悠，发现一个有趣的网站，<a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/\" target=\"_blank\">www.sentex.net/~mwandel/</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/gallery/old_blog_file/20110224210918_1.jpg\" alt=\"网页截图\" width=\"438\" height=\"420\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">首页上这位大叔就是Matthias Wandel，这家伙是个木工世家出生，他爸爸也是做木工的，除了木工典型制作的桌、椅、床之外，还做了很多了不起的稀奇玩意，下面列举几个：（一下图片全部来自<a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/\">http://www.sentex.net</a>）</p>\n<figure style=\"width: 178px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\" \" title=\"木制三脚架\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/built/wood_tripod.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"178\" height=\"268\" /><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">木制三脚架</figcaption></figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/built/practical.html\" target=\"_blank\">全木质的相机三脚架，这家伙懂摄影</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/photo/panohead.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"209\" height=\"233\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/photo/panos.html\" target=\"_blank\">自制全景云台</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/organ/playing_organ.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"384\" height=\"285\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/organ/organ.html\" target=\"_blank\">全木质的管风琴，这家伙懂音乐</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/tech/changer_overview.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"379\" height=\"232\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/tech/changer.html\" target=\"_blank\">全木质的CD换片机，这家伙懂机电</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/tech/scanning_camera.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/tech/scanner.html\" target=\"_blank\">木质扫描相机，这家伙懂光学、软件，已经佩服的五体投地</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/cannon/marble_musket.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"495\" height=\"91\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/cannon/air_gun.html\" target=\"_blank\">自制气枪</a></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/cannon/m_and_m's.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"261\" height=\"197\" /><img src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/cannon/m_and_m_penetrates.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"255\" height=\"184\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/cannon/air_gun.html\" target=\"_blank\">用M&amp;M豆当子弹，威力不小啊，三夹板打穿了！</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"//www.sentex.net/~mwandel/photo/tossing-tikka-lights.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/~mwandel/photo/night-photography.html\" target=\"_blank\">这不是去年各大摄影杂志流行的光绘嘛，这家伙似乎很久以前就玩过了</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">等等一些，大家自己去看看这网站吧。不佩服不行，什么叫动手能力！这家伙网站结构也简明易懂，没有任何的装饰，只是要表达的内容平实的展示，比那些什么门户网站打开满眼flash飞舞看的舒服多了。</p>\n<p>就这些制作品，我已经很难想象需要多少方面的知识了。除此之外，他首页上还有个股票经营模拟游戏的链接……呵呵，总之挺有趣的，自己看看吧<a href=\"http://www.sentex.net/\">http://www.sentex.net</a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2011/02/interesting-site-carpenter/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}